---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = new Date();
const fmt = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("en-US", { month: "long", day: "numeric", year: "numeric" });
---
<Layout
  title="Now — Pedro Mansan"
  description="What I'm focused on right now."
  current="now"
>
  <section class="hero" style="margin-top: 0;">
    <h1>Now</h1>
    <div class="role">A snapshot of what I'm doing this month</div>
  </section>

  <section class="prose" style="margin-top: 56px;">
    <p>
      I'm in the third semester of Computer Science at UTFPR, in Marechal Cândido
      Rondon, Paraná. Most evenings end with a problem set or a system design
      exercise.
    </p>

    <p>
      Looking for a full stack mid-level role, remote, US/EU teams. The kind of
      product where the interesting problems are in the database and the auth
      layer rather than the brand color.
    </p>

    <p>
      Writing up a few of the systems I built at Mindz over the last four years —
      see <a href="/writing/">/writing</a> for what's in progress. Refining spoken
      English for technical interviews on the side.
    </p>

    <p class="muted" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px;">
      Last updated: {fmt.format(lastUpdated)}
    </p>

    <p class="muted" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px;">
      Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nownownow.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
